No. 11M28. Brandie Atkins, Administrator of the Estate of William O. Atkins, Deceased, Petitioner v. City of Chicago, Illinois, et al. 565 U.S. 939, 132 S. Ct. 444,

181 L. Ed. 2d 253,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7422. October 11, 2011.
